### Step 1: Request Device Code
POST https://login.microsoftonline.com/consumers/oauth2/v2.0/devicecode
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

client_id=48d9762f-fc4c-4d0a-9670-a37904a29cf2&scope=api://48d9762f-fc4c-4d0a-9670-a37904a29cf2/Weather.Read

### Step 2: Poll for Access Token (replace YOUR_DEVICE_CODE)
POST https://login.microsoftonline.com/consumers/oauth2/v2.0/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=device_code&client_id=48d9762f-fc4c-4d0a-9670-a37904a29cf2&device_code=YOUR_DEVICE_CODE

### Step 3: Call Protected API Endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/weatherforecast
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>